    "longBusinessSummary": "Marketing Home Group Company for Trading Company operates as a trading company in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, the United Arab Emirates, the People's Republic of China, Kingdom of Spain, and Arab Republic of Egypt. The company engages in the construction of prefabricated buildings on-site; renovation of residential and non-residential buildings; wholesale of oud, incense, perfumes, bricks, blocks, tiles, stone, marble, ceramics, porcelain, sanitary ware and accessories, water heaters, and tanks; retail trade of basins, toilets, bathtubs, sauna equipment, electrical appliances and fittings, marble, natural and artificial stone, ceramics, porcelain, chandeliers, lighting products, and accessories. It is also involved in the operation of storage facilities for all types of goods; marble cutting and sawing; manufacture of marble products, such as kitchens, sinks, antiques, basins, statues, sculptures, and paintings; and manufacture of air conditioning ducts and duct accessories. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.",
